Package: veritas
Title: Toolkit for working with veritas data
Type: Package
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2021-10-04
Author: Alexandre Naud [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Alexandre Naud <alexandre.naud@gmail.com>
Description: 
    Set of functions to load, transform and calculate 
    variables from data generated using the veritas tool.
    See https://doi.org/10.1016/j.healthplace.2020.102454 for further
    description of this tool.
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: 
    cli, 
    igraph,
    magrittr
Suggests: 
    rmarkdown,
    knitr
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/alex-naud/veritas-r
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
VignetteBuilder: knitr
